    "en": {
      "title": "Gold worth Rs.4.7 crore was seized",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "16 gold biscuits and 4 gold bars worth Rs 47 million illegally brought into the country have been seized by the Customs at Katunayake Airport and one person has been arrested.",
        "2 kg of gold weighing 98 grams, which was brought from Dubai at 1 am today, has been seized.",
        "Deputy Commissioner of Customs Wijeratna Bhandara conducted the customs investigation and ordered the confiscation of the illegally imported gold.",
        "The Deputy Commissioner of Customs also ordered the arrested 35-year-old man from Thematagoda to pay a fine of Rs 50,000."
      ],
